  "instructions": [
    "Preheat grill to medium-high heat.",
    "In a large bowl, whisk together olive oil, paprika, cumin, coriander, salt, and black pepper.",
    "Add the chicken cubes to the bowl and toss to coat with the spice mixture.",
    "Thread 3-4 chicken cubes onto each skewer.",
    "Brush the grill grates with olive oil to prevent sticking.",
    "Grill the kebabs for 8-10 minutes per side, or until the chicken is cooked through and crispy.",
    "Brush the kebabs with lemon juice during the last minute of grilling.",
    "Serve hot, garnished with fresh parsley or cilantro if desired."
